 boundary\nconditions are developed and included in a general manner with the continuum\nkinetic algorithm for bounded plasma simulations. These are the first continuum\nkinetic simulations using self-consistent, wall emission boundary conditions\nwith broad applicability across a variety of regimes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2018 17:45:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-17"}
