uide the development\nof a physical model to describe the long-term X-ray variability of this and\nother similarly behaved X-ray binary systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Sep 2018 18:19:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
